    Hello! I appreciate you taking the time to consider me for a role. Here you'll find my resume, links to my professional profiles, and some information about what I'm looking for in my next role.
  </p>
  <section>
    <h3>Links</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/resume">View my resume on this site</a></li>
      <li><a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Download my resume (PDF)</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/scavender" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn Profile</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h3>What I'm Looking For</h3>
    <p>I am passionate about working for companies of any size that emphasize learning and autonomy. Ideally I'd like to continue being full-stack and leaning more into AI/LLM utilization.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
